Telkom has revealed its Big Deal for January 2019. The deal offers clients free value and devices when they sign up for a 10Mbps uncapped DSL or fibre package. Users will then receive: It must be noted that a fair usage policy applies to the uncapped broadband account. In its terms and conditions, Telkom also states that for the fibre package, users must be on Openserve infrastructure. Fibre networks such as Vumatel are not included in the deal. The deal is valid until 31 January 2019, or while stocks last, said Telkom. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">ï»¿</span>